description: Beautifully renovated in 2022, this spacious 2-bedroom condo offers modern living in one of Tysons' most desirable gated communitiesThe Rotonda. Step inside to discover an updated interior featuring a sleek kitchen, contemporary finishes, and thoughtfully designed spaces. Located on a lush 34-acre resort-style property, the Rotonda offers unmatched amenities including indoor and outdoor pools, a state-of-the-art fitness center, yoga studio, tennis and pickleball courts, walking trails, a putting green, dog park, convenience store, playgrounds, and more. Residents enjoy 24/7 security, three elevators per building, electric car chargers, and ample gathering spaces like a resident lounge, library, and multipurpose room. All just minutes from the Silver Line Metro, Tysons Corner Center, Whole Foods, Capital One Center, 495, and I-66
